                    <h2 class="more-info-text">If you, or one of your employees, need to complete DOT drug/alcohol testing for preemployment, return to duty, follow-up, post-accident, reasonable suspicion or a random selection, all of OnSITE Drug Testing and Consulting’s employees are trained and certified to properly collect and process federally regulated specimens for the DOT.</h2>
